    JUnit reporter output single failed assertion node per test case

    Ideally JUnit tools would handle multiple failures per test case,
    but they don't, so here we are.

    Closes #1919

diff --git a/src/catch2/reporters/catch_reporter_junit.cpp b/src/catch2/reporters/catch_reporter_junit.cpp
